sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Pengguna
  participant Browser as Pelayar
  participant Server as Pelayan
  participant Queue as Giliran
  participant Worker as Pekerja
  participant DB as PangkalanData
  participant Cache as Cache
  participant Dashboard as PapanPemuka

  Pengguna->>Pelayar: Pilih & hantar fail
  Pelayar->>Pelayan: POST /upload
  Pelayan->>Pelayan: Validate, IMB scan
  Pelayan->>Pelayan: Store raw file
  Pelayan->>Giliran: Enqueue job
  Giliran->>Pekerja: Job pulled
  Pekerja->>Pekerja: Parse & transform
  Pekerja->>PangkalanData: Insert/Update
  Pekerja->>Cache: Update aggregates
  Pelayan->>PapanPemuka: Notify / Invalidate cache
  PapanPemuka->>PangkalanData: Query data
  PapanPemuka->>Pengguna: Render charts
